Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.51,0:00:03.44,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Flowing water has no form.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.44,0:00:05.33,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}A blowing wind can't be seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.33,0:00:07.28,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}All cases can be freely deduced!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.28,0:00:09.05,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Today, we're at a coffee shop by a road on a hill.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.05,0:00:11.24,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Was it an accident or a case that came flying in?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.24,0:00:12.83,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.83,0:00:14.63,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.63,0:00:16.43,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}{\fad(0,84)}His name? Detective Conan!
