Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.88,0:00:52.50,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Color Key\NReiko Hirayama\N \NExecutive Producer\NHiroaki Kobayashi
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.93,0:01:03.43,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Planning Support\NToyohiko Okuyama\NMitome Asai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.68,0:01:07.35,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief Director\NKenji Kodama\N \NDirector\NYasuichiro Yamamoto
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.74,0:01:21.49,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Producers\NMichihiko Suwa\N(Yomiuri TV)\NMasahito Yoshioka\N(Tokyo Movie)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.00,0:02:00.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't walk another step.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.15,0:02:01.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.96,0:02:03.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a little further...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.90,0:02:07.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,According to Doc's map, it's right around this curve coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.04,0:02:08.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You can do it, Genta-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.55,0:02:13.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, maybe taking the bus would've been faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.34,0:02:14.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.27,0:02:15.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to be treated to lunch,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.91,0:02:18.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,so if we take the bus it would render everything meaningless!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.35,0:02:20.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean you just wanted to save bus fare?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.15,0:02:23.66,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}What a tight-fisted brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.16,0:02:35.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... It's supposed to be around here...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.25,0:02:38.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Mitsuhiko, isn't that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.68,0:02:47.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"P-e-a-c-h S-u-n-d-a-y..."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.85,0:02:49.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the place after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.76,0:02:51.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mitsuhiko-{\i1}kun{\i0}, you can read English?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.35,0:02:54.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm bilingual.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.31,0:02:59.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, let's go inside. I'm starved.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.09,0:03:00.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, let's!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.65,0:03:05.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.81,0:03:09.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, we...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.27,0:03:11.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Detective Boys, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.03,0:03:13.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to meet with Dr. Agasa here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.80,0:03:14.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This way please.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.96,0:03:16.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,- Right.\N- Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.92,0:03:19.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm starved.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.97,0:03:24.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi there, welcome to our shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.70,0:03:26.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Agasa called me about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.93,0:03:30.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He said he'll be a little late, so eat anything you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.01,0:03:32.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That looks yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.94,0:03:36.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Genta-{\i1}kun{\i0}, ladies first!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.02,0:03:38.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Of course! Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.25,0:03:40.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.28,0:03:41.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.65,0:03:42.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.27,0:03:46.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Ohara. I have a reservation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.15,0:03:47.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, please come this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.40,0:03:51.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They say the house specialty is great, it's the peach sundae.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.48,0:03:53.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the owner's original.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.04,0:03:54.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have that, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.58,0:03:55.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.25,0:03:58.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What would you like, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.08,0:04:01.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The same as the rest of you is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.26,0:04:04.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, four peach sundaes please!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.41,0:04:05.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.14,0:04:08.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That looks yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.33,0:04:12.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,- It's really yummy!\N- It sure is!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.59,0:04:14.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you gonna eat, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.84,0:04:16.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take it, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.68,0:04:17.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Genta-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.50,0:04:19.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be a waste if the ice cream were to melt...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.63,0:04:21.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that? Leaflets again?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.88,0:04:23.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a rush job.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.64,0:04:27.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They're going to be passing it out at the shopping center {any better wording for shoutengai?} this coming Sunday.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.55,0:04:28.10,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazuo Ohara (52)\NOhara Design — President
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.40,0:04:31.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You should just refuse such a cheap-paying job.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.46,0:04:32.39,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Toru Aida (35)\NOhara Design — Designer
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.10,0:04:32.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.85,0:04:36.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the kind of job that leads to a stable income! Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.72,0:04:38.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.95,0:04:43.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you think about the you-know-what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.78,0:04:47.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how many times you ask me,\Nmy answer will not change.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.18,0:04:50.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it money you want?\NIf so, I'll increase the amount...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.30,0:04:53.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think you can,\Nwith what work you're doing now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.30,0:04:56.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe not just yet,\Nbut I promise that someday I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.53,0:04:58.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There you go again!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.01,0:04:59.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you do something about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.52,0:05:00.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about persistent.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.42,0:05:06.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to spend the rest of my life making leaflets!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.23,0:05:09.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Working with you is ruining my talent!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.90,0:05:11.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Take it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.38,0:05:14.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bet you don't have any on the pamphlets
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.08,0:05:15.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,of the resort hotel that I'm asking you to work on this time.{?}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.35,0:05:20.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, as for that, I'll take the job as pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.60,0:05:23.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't handle it anyway if I leave, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.64,0:05:24.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.94,0:05:28.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I promise to finish these leaflets before I leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.56,0:05:35.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get started. You're in a hurry, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.87,0:05:41.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to the restroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.99,0:05:56.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.97,0:05:58.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Both of them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.55,0:05:59.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.87,0:06:02.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mitsuhiko, what's your second recommendation?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.80,0:06:05.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll get a stomach-ache if you eat too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.40,0:06:07.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.81,0:06:11.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you so.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.95,0:06:14.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I gotta go to the restroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.83,0:06:16.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Genta, someone's in the restroom right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.20,0:06:24.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Somebody's inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.73,0:06:27.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That was good!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.70,0:06:29.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's indeed worth recommending.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.97,0:06:32.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Genta, someone was inside, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.35,0:06:33.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.60,0:06:37.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know who's in there,\Nbut he doesn't answer when I knock!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.67,0:06:39.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,- I'm gonna explode...\N- Oh, he just came out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.94,0:06:41.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.11,0:06:42.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, a customer...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.03,0:06:45.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay, I'm saved!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.88,0:06:48.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're ordering seconds, get me some too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.06,0:06:52.57,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.30,0:06:56.46,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}He's using his right hand this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.46,0:06:58.19,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}He's ambidextrous.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.74,0:07:00.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.91,0:07:02.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Dr. Agasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.43,0:07:04.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.81,0:07:06.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're all digging in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.36,0:07:08.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, eat all you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.94,0:07:11.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I won the raffle at the shopping center!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.48,0:07:13.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright then, I'll take...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.06,0:07:17.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,a hot fudge sundae, custard à la mode\Nand strawberry shortcake!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.05,0:07:19.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How's your stomach?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.60,0:07:21.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.41,0:07:25.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at that bus!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.05,0:07:27.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what it is. It's beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.09,0:07:28.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It really is!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.30,0:07:38.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I dropped my lighter. I'll go check.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.27,0:07:43.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want it done by sundown. I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.77,0:07:45.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.45,0:07:54.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}, whatcha having?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.50,0:07:55.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'll have coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.15,0:07:56.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.97,0:07:58.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, well, I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.42,0:08:01.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What the?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.90,0:08:05.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.03,0:08:24.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means that you just happened to leave your seat, so you were spared?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.90,0:08:28.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I just happened to go to the restroom to look for my lighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.21,0:08:31.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness you were spared...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.58,0:08:34.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're the president of Ohara Design.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.83,0:08:38.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The office is located at the top of the hill, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.65,0:08:39.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.75,0:08:44.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I found the driver of the truck!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.22,0:08:47.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll be right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.85,0:08:56.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you park your car part-way up the hill, like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.05,0:08:57.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and make your delivery?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.86,0:09:02.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, I usually park on a flat place uphill,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.91,0:09:02.66,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Jiro Kobayashi (25)\NExpress Delivery Driver
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.25,0:09:04.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but that car was parked here today,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.99,0:09:07.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,so I had no choice but to park in front of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.02,0:09:10.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I made sure my emergency brake was engaged,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.63,0:09:13.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and had the gear in reverse just to be safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.29,0:09:16.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito-{\i1}san{\i0}, I went to the site right away
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.79,0:09:20.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and checked the driver's seat, but the emergency brake was disengaged!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.76,0:09:23.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible! Please check more carefully!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.91,0:09:26.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I know I pulled my emergency brake and engaged it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.43,0:09:27.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course he's lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.05,0:09:30.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Aida-{\i1}kun{\i0} was...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.83,0:09:33.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Aida-{\i1}kun{\i0} was my precious right-hand man!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.39,0:09:38.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Without him, my company is finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.39,0:09:42.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! Did someone die?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.01,0:09:43.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,President!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.03,0:09:45.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Segawa-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.10,0:09:47.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing in a place like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.28,0:09:50.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't deposit the money today,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.92,0:09:52.71,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Michiko Segawa (46)\NOhara Design — Clerk
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.40,0:09:53.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,they're going to stop shipment of the goods!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.02,0:09:54.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.23,0:09:56.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But this is no time for something that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.61,0:09:59.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Aida-{\i1}kun{\i0} passed away...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.78,0:10:02.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He was in an accident...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.46,0:10:03.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.88,0:10:16.31,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Strange. What could that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.88,0:10:19.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.05,0:10:20.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.00,0:10:28.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! This place is off-limits!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.48,0:10:30.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot something in the restroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.14,0:10:36.11,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}He was licking his finger when he first came out of the restroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.90,0:10:38.47,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I wonder if he got hurt in the restroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.34,0:10:40.86,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.82,0:10:57.77,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Blood stains?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.28,0:11:04.80,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}These are traces of a hand touching the frame from outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.27,0:11:11.24,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.89,0:11:14.92,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}The blood got here when he came back from outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.79,0:11:18.09,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}That's why there was no answer when Genta knocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.62,0:11:22.99,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Ohara-{\i1}san{\i0} wasn't in the restroom then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.56,0:11:29.43,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}He hurt his left hand when he was outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.90,0:11:34.65,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}That's why he held the pencil in his right after coming back...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.63,0:11:40.49,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}But where did he go,\Nand what was he trying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.78,0:11:56.40,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Before the accident, Ohara-{\i1}san{\i0}\Nseemed very concerned about the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.37,0:12:00.11,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Did he have to go out at a certain time?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.78,0:12:02.52,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Time...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.59,0:12:07.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Conan, where did you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.66,0:12:10.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I just went to get something I forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.21,0:12:18.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Does anyone remember at what time the accident occurred?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.70,0:12:22.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,About 2:10, right after Dr. Agasa got here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.50,0:12:24.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,2:10...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.76,0:12:27.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's one at 2:07...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.25,0:12:28.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.68,0:12:29.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.06,0:12:34.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what route the bus that left here just before the accident took?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.96,0:12:36.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it should be coming back soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.95,0:12:41.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's supposed to make a circuit from the complex back to the shopping center.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.20,0:12:50.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why was that bus stopped?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.55,0:12:52.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the end of the line,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.90,0:12:55.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,so the buses take a break for 5 to 10\Nminutes to get back on schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.70,0:13:06.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.81,0:13:08.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do we have a case?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.21,0:13:11.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No fair, Conan! You're always hogging the clues!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.52,0:13:12.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.30,0:13:24.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I'd like to ask you kids some questions too,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.70,0:13:25.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,so come here, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.97,0:13:27.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.67,0:13:30.60,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Piano wire?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.26,0:13:35.70,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Aha! I've figured it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.65,0:13:38.39,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}This is a homicide!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.80,0:13:40.15,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}And the killer is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.65,0:13:42.15,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I'm sure it's him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.33,0:13:48.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.99,0:13:50.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.20,0:13:53.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have some urgent business to attend to,\Nso I'd like to be excused for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.82,0:13:55.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't allow that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.15,0:13:58.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to go make a bank transfer to one of my clients.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.90,0:14:03.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,30 minutes—no, 20 minutes, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.11,0:14:07.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Has he been questioned?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.58,0:14:10.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, briefly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.31,0:14:11.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you can go, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.75,0:14:13.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.75,0:14:15.00,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.00,0:14:17.95,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}If he's released, he'll go and get rid of all the evidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.08,0:14:19.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Doc!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.62,0:14:22.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a homicide!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.49,0:14:24.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.28,0:14:25.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Move your lips like always for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.98,0:14:27.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.28,0:14:28.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait just a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.99,0:14:30.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who, me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.99,0:14:34.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I can't have you leave just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.32,0:14:36.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.32,0:14:38.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a murder case!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.24,0:14:44.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.57,0:14:46.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Agasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.61,0:14:49.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Will outsiders stay out of this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.65,0:14:52.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it. Let's at least hear him out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.25,0:14:54.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Agasa-{\i1}san{\i0}, do you have a lead?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.74,0:14:57.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I not only have a lead, I have proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.70,0:14:58.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ohara-{\i1}san{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.08,0:15:02.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have proof that you are the killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.71,0:15:06.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.39,0:15:09.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how you look at it, this is an accident caused by the carelessness of the driver
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.72,0:15:11.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,whose truck crashed into the shop!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.33,0:15:12.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.76,0:15:15.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us hear, Agasa-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.19,0:15:20.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well. Then first, let me explain the trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.90,0:15:21.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.46,0:15:26.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a busy man! I don't have time\Nto waste listening to a made-up story!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.86,0:15:28.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ohara-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.41,0:15:31.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll just be a short while, so let's hear him out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.45,0:15:35.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.30,0:15:40.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ohara-{\i1}san{\i0}, you parked your car\Nat the top of the hill
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.70,0:15:43.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,where the delivery truck always parks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.93,0:15:47.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you asked Aida-{\i1}san{\i0} to come with you\Nto the coffee shop at the bottom of the hill.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.55,0:15:50.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And then you made him sit by the window,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.20,0:15:52.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,so that he couldn't see the slope from his side.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.45,0:15:54.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.22,0:15:56.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.73,0:15:59.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't make him sit by the window so that he couldn't see the slope!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.81,0:16:02.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The place he sat just happened to be by the window!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.61,0:16:03.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.85,0:16:08.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you left a while later,\Nin the middle of negotiation,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.63,0:16:11.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,pretending to go to the restroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.45,0:16:14.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't pretending! I really went to the restroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.83,0:16:16.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.05,0:16:23.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Genta-{\i1}kun{\i0} here says he kept knocking on the door, but you didn't answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.34,0:16:26.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! My stomach was so sore, I thought I'd die!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.67,0:16:27.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.60,0:16:32.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Back then, you snuck out of the restroom window,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.00,0:16:34.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and went over to the delivery truck.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.02,0:16:39.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You placed a wooden wedge that you had set up beforehand
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.38,0:16:41.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,in front of the front tires of the truck.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.49,0:16:43.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.61,0:16:46.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would I do something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.00,0:16:51.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a trick to make it look like you weren't committing the crime!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.18,0:16:55.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You attached piano wire to the wooden wedge,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.31,0:17:00.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and then tied it to the back of the bus\Nwhich was parked there for time adjustment.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.40,0:17:05.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you shifted the gear of the delivery truck to neutral,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.25,0:17:07.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and released the emergency brake.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.77,0:17:11.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You then returned to the coffee shop as if nothing had happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.98,0:17:14.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When the time came\Nand the bus started to move,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.52,0:17:16.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,the wedge would come off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.42,0:17:23.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That way, the delivery truck would roll down the hill all by itself!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.10,0:17:27.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All you had to do next was to wait for the bus to pass the coffee shop
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.80,0:17:29.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and get out of the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.00,0:17:33.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,by pretending to go to the restroom to look for your lighter!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.68,0:17:37.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.09,0:17:39.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The thing that was shimmering at the back of the bus
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.23,0:17:40.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,was the piano wire!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.81,0:17:43.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. And that wedge is right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.79,0:17:46.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.39,0:17:49.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.21,0:17:50.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.92,0:17:55.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a plain piece of wood...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.15,0:17:58.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The wooden wedge is dragged along by the bus,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.56,0:18:02.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and shatters as it bounces on the pavement.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.03,0:18:03.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what's left of the wedge.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.66,0:18:07.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The car, which was accelerating because the road was on a hill,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.39,0:18:09.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,crashed into the window of the coffee shop,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.22,0:18:12.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and burst inside, just as you had planned!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.62,0:18:24.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Aida-{\i1}san{\i0} was hit and killed by the truck from behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.92,0:18:28.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's say... Let's say the trick is as you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.34,0:18:31.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But do you have proof that I did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.57,0:18:33.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Proof? I sure do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.20,0:18:40.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This was your mistake: you hurt your finger tying the piano wire to the bus.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.01,0:18:45.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My hand got stuck on the restroom doorknob!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.00,0:18:49.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The delivery truck can be operated one-handed,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.89,0:18:52.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,so you didn't leave any blood stains there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.07,0:18:54.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But when you re-entered through the restroom window,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.36,0:18:56.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,you touched it and left blood stains on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.74,0:19:04.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's some blood on the inside of the restroom window.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.99,0:19:10.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,After returning from the restroom,\Nyou continued making arrangements.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.65,0:19:15.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But since you hurt your left hand,\Nyou held the pencil in your right hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.45,0:19:21.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan witnessed you licking your left hand occasionally.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.26,0:19:23.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right, Conan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.34,0:19:29.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I hurt my finger.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.37,0:19:33.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But like I just said, I scratched it on the doorknob.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.85,0:19:35.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Can something like that be considered proof?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.97,0:19:37.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Can it, officer?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.52,0:19:38.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,H-He's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.97,0:19:40.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.58,0:19:46.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, if you insist I'm the killer,\Nshow me concrete evidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.37,0:19:47.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.88,0:19:56.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a glove with a strange pattern in the car!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.90,0:20:11.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is the meaning of this, Ohara-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.10,0:20:15.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If the piano wire on the bus is checked,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.00,0:20:18.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,your blood should also be detected on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.10,0:20:22.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The blood stains from your wound in the restroom
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.93,0:20:26.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and the blood stains on the glove in the car should match exactly!{bluffed this a bit, couldn't make sense of either}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.91,0:20:28.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The blood stain on the frame of the restroom window
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.75,0:20:31.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,shows that you held the frame from outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.46,0:20:37.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore, your blood stains are also on the piano wire tied to the bus...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.30,0:20:41.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How are you going to explain all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.85,0:20:46.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How about it, Ohara-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.36,0:20:52.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I did him in.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.05,0:20:59.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.30,0:21:03.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Aida dared to forget everything I did for him until now,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.21,0:21:06.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and betrayed me by saying he was going to quit working for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.05,0:21:12.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If he were to quit, my company would go bankrupt...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.41,0:21:15.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If it were going to go bankrupt anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.32,0:21:17.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I figured I should kill him\Nand make it look like an accident,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.89,0:21:22.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and at least get a hold of his\Nlife insurance money as compensation.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.23,0:21:27.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,To tell the truth, I hadn't made my mind up until we were at the coffee shop...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.00,0:21:36.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But he had the nerve to say he was going to take away a big job that I found as retirement pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.50,0:21:39.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What a thing to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.73,0:21:42.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm very sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.88,0:23:22.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,0)\a6}"Peach Sunday — Renovated and Reopening"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.21,0:23:26.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much, Agasa-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.70,0:23:29.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you, my innocence has been proven.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.77,0:23:35.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No problem, no big thing, I can handle things like this with my hands tied behind my back!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.08,0:23:38.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the one who taught the famous high-school detective Shin'ichi Kudo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.08,0:23:43.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,the skills of being a detective, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.00,0:23:45.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.11,0:23:47.58,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Geez. You sure can talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.38,0:23:49.40,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Oh well.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.15,0:23:52.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.10,0:24:02.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's dated 10 years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.57,0:24:06.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is 10 years before Misaki-{\i1}san{\i0} got married!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.90,0:24:09.81,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.13,0:24:17.99,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Could there be more than one killer?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.06,0:24:21.37,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}What is this a piece of?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.80,0:24:23.77,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Just as I thought... This is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.08,0:24:30.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Next Conan:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.13,0:24:35.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's Hint: Bust
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.33,0:24:37.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Next time, a dignified tale!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.33,0:24:37.20,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,kakuchō/hanashi
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.20,0:24:38.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Big stomachs roaming free?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.20,0:24:38.96,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,ikakuchō
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.20,0:24:38.96,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,hanashigai
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.96,0:24:39.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Sounds great!
